{"tid":1034640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做得八達通查飛狗嘅都係毒柒醜臭窮","createTime":"2019-02-24T05:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:31:25.000Z","uid":170365,"like":10,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a381b6ec7d4abd82ab1de32d269c809a22af43a4","tid":1034640,"uid":170365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"睇下呢兩隻垃圾查飛狗<br />\n身形己經痴肥到成隻豬噉 個樣又毒又柒<br />\n兩個企喺閘到 睥撚住啲乘客以為自己做緊地鐵特攻噉<br />\n見幾個賓賓走咗入去重要走去查賓賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果食白果冇生意做 星期日呢啲同女女拍拖嘅日子 呢兩條肥柒醜毒撚就喺到做查飛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵你哋做狗畀人屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNcnNc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNcnNc8.jpg&h=3feb5c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGmsdS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGmsdS5.jpg&h=2424ba19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNSvbEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNSvbEM.jpg&h=cb482e85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39c207e5b1c38fe64654bc5e24533d86adb79a5b","tid":1034640,"uid":39470,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"啱啱俾人罰左幾錢？"},{"pid":"df1287bb155f47774b71468ff63ea672e80b72ee","tid":1034640,"uid":170365,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"39c207e5b1c38fe64654bc5e24533d86adb79a5b","tid":1034640,"uid":39470,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"啱啱俾人罰左幾錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"又唔係用長者/學生八達通 響都唔響一下<br />\n佢又點會敢走嚟check我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢過嚟check我實屌柒佢"},{"pid":"42f73156c33189d36eced2ae42bea48c0f3640a0","tid":1034640,"uid":189386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"人地得罪左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm